, Internationale de l'imaginaire, entre autres). Il est président de la Maison des Cultures du monde à Paris et dirige la revue Internationale de l'imaginaire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Theater / General.2bisacsh1 aDuvignaud, par jean, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276371355740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763713557423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763713557/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles